divs: Sighting DetailsIn May 2 2009 with my telescope in the backyard around 10.15p.m.the north to the southwest i see very bright light around 1500 ft 2000ft focus the telescope i see one sphere with somenthing four corner points structure stacked one each other and the middle the structure one line with very bright line red color when pass over me no sound nothing no more details move fast and no easy focus with telescope very strange object. for my is no the first time strange object move over the sky in Puerto Rico.
